ate=July 7, 2013 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=July 7, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=wlbz2>{{cite news |url=http://www.wlbz2.com/news/article/248868/3/Maine-fire-crews-assist-in-Quebec-train-explosion |title=Maine fire crews assist in Quebec train explosion |publisher=[[WLBZ]] |date=July 6, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709172920/http://www.wlbz2.com/news/article/248868/3/Maine-fire-crews-assist-in-Quebec-train-explosion |archivedate=July 9, 2013 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=gm-path>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/path-to-disaster-how-lac-megantics-relationship-with-rail-has-long-been-fraying/article13085112/ |title=Path to disaster: How Lac-M\u00e9gantic's relationship with rail has long been fraying |newspaper=The Globe and Mail |date=July 6, 2013 |accessdate=July 10, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=jm-engineer>{{cite news |url=http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2013/07/08/lac-megantic-tom-harding-introuvable |author1=\u00c9tienne, Anne-Lovely |author2=B\u00e9lisle, Sarah |title=Explosion Lac-M\u00e9gantic: Employ\u00e9 de la MMA Lac-M\u00e9gantic: conducteur muet |publisher=le Journal de Montr\u00e9al |date=July 8, 2013 |accessdate=July 9, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=oc-nantes-fd>{{cite news |url=https://ottawacitizen.com/news/Nantes+fire+chief+confirms+late+night+fire+before+M%C3%A9gantic/8631340/story.html |title=Nantes fire chief confirms late-night fire before explosion |author=Adam Kovac, [[Montreal Gazette]] |publisher=[[Postmedia]] |date=July 8, 2013 |accessdate=July 8, 2013 |language=}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=rtl>{{cite news |url=http://www.rtl.fr/actualites/info/international/article/explosion-du-train-au-quebec-il-n-y-avait-pas-de-chauffeur-c-etait-un-train-teleguide-7762942252 |title=Qu\u00e9bec : l'explosion du train a ravag\u00e9 Lac-M\u00e9gantic |publisher=[[RTL (French radio)|RTL]] |date=July 7, 2013 |accessdate=July 7, 2013 | language=French}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=oc>{{cite news |url=https://ottawacitizen.com/business/Explosions+rock+Quebec+town+after+train+carrying+crude+derails/8625450/story.html |title=Quebec police say 5 dead from oil train derailment, 40 missing |date=July 7, 2013 |newspaper=[[Ottawa Citizen]] |accessdate=July 7, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130712031943/http://www.ottawacitizen.com/business/Explosions+rock+Quebec+town+after+train+carrying+crude+derails/8625450/story.html |archivedate=July 12, 2013 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=ntsb>{{cite web |url=http://www.ntsb.gov/doclib/reports/2012/RAR1201.pdf |title=Derailment of CN Freight Train U70691-18 With Subsequent Hazardous Materials Release and Fire |date=June 19, 2009 |publisher=[[National Transportation Safety Board]] |accessdate=July 8, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<!--unused\n<ref name=reuters-bdn>{{cite news|author1=P.J. Huffstutter |author2=Richard Valdmanis |agency=Reuters |url=http://bangordailynews.com/2013/07/09/news/world-news/how-a-train-ran-away-and-devastated-a-canadian-town/ |title=How a train ran away and devastated a Canadian town |newspaper=Bangor Daily News |date=July 6, 2013 |accessdate=July 10, 2013}}</ref>-->\n\n<!--<ref name=spec-engineer>[http://www.thespec.com/news-story/3884006-engineer-rushed-to-haul-tankers-away-from-quebec-train-crash/]\"Engineer rushed to haul tankers away from Quebec train crash,\" Hamilton Spectator, July 9, 2013. Retrieved July 9, 2013</ref>-->\n\n<ref name=star-trib>{{cite news |url=http://www.startribune.com/business/214699171.html |title=Blast in Quebec exposes risks of shipping crude oil by rail |author=David Shaffer |date=July 9, 2013 |publisher=Star-Tribune (Minneapolis-St Paul) |accessdate=July 9, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<!--<ref name=tcrules>{{cite web|url=http://www.tc.gc.ca/eng/railsafety/rules-tco93-167.htm |title=Canadian Railway Operating Rules, section 112 |publisher=Transport Canada |accessdate=July 9, 2013}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name=tribune-plusjamais>{{cite news|url=http://www.lapresse.ca/la-tribune/perspectives/201307/07/01-4668564-plus-jamais.php |title=Plus jamais! |author=Luc Larochelle |publisher=La Tribune (Sherbrooke) |date=July 7, 2013 |accessdate=July 10, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=tribune-burglars>{{cite news|url=http://www.lapresse.ca/la-tribune/actualites/201307/09/01-4669066-lac-megantic-serie-de-vols-dans-les-domiciles-abandonnes.php |title=Lac-M\u00e9gantic: s\u00e9rie de vols dans les domiciles abandonn\u00e9s |author=J\u00e9r\u00f4me Gaudreau |publisher=La Tribune (Sherbrooke) |language=French |date=July 9, 2013 |accessdate=July 9, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=tribune-tourisme>{{cite news|url=http://www.lapresse.ca/la-tribune/actualites/201307/09/01-4669219-la-mairesse-lance-un-appel-aux-touristes.php |title=La mairesse lance un appel aux touristes |publisher=La Tribune (Sherbrooke) |language=French |date=July 9, 2013 |accessdate=July 9, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<!--<ref name=wsj>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424127887323368704578593562819939112?mod=WSJ_Opinion_LEADTop |title=Stephens: Can Environmentalists Think? |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |date=July 8, 2013 |accessdate=July 9, 2013}} {{subscription required}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name=vansun>{{cite news |url=https://vancouversun.com/news/Devastated+LacMegantic+begins+work+week+with+core+shattered/8629575/story.html |title=Devastated Lac-Megantic begins work week, with about 40 people still missing after train disaster (with video) |date=July 8, 2013 |newspaper=[[The Vancouver Sun]] |accessdate=July 8, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=journaldemontreal130708>{{cite news|url=http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2013/07/08/lac-megantic-tom-harding-introuvable |title=Lac-M\u00e9gantic: le conducteur du train reste muet |date=July 8, 2013 |publisher=[[Journal de Montr\u00e9al]] |accessdate=July 11, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=vancouversun09>{{cite news|url=https://vancouversun.com/mobile/news/national-news/silent+train+engineer+centre+storm/8637412/story.html |title=The silent train engineer at the centre of the storm |newspaper=[[The Vancouver Sun]] |accessdate=July 11, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=quatrevingtdixhuit01>{{cite news |url=http://www.985fm.ca/national/nouvelles/des-etincelles-avant-l-explosion-251284.html |title=Des \u00e9tincelles avant l'explosion |publisher=[[CHMP-FM]] 98,5 Montreal |accessdate=July 11, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714120522/http://www.985fm.ca/national/nouvelles/des-etincelles-avant-l-explosion-251284.html |archivedate=July 14, 2013 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=nb}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://montrealgazette.com/news/Lives+lost+Remembering+M%C3%A9gantic+victims/8654646/story.html Lives lost: Remembering Lac-M\u00e9gantic\u2019s victims], biographical sketches of those killed in the derailment, at the [[Montreal Gazette]]\n*[http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/rapports-reports/rail/2013/r13d0054/r13d0054-r-es.asp Lac-M\u00e9gantic runaway train and derailment investigation (summary version of the TSB report)]\n*[http://www.tsb.gc.ca/eng/rapports-reports/rail/2013/r13d0054/r13d0054.asp Railway Investigation Report (long version of the TSB report)]\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wVMNspPc8Zc Lac-M\u00e9gantic MMA Train Accident - July 6, 2013]. Video from TSB Canada documenting findings from the TSB investigation of the Lac-M\u00e9gantic derailment.\n*[https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/dispatches-from-a-disaster/article20148699 Audio: Train engineer and railway company talk as Lac-M\u00e9gantic burns]. Audio and text of conversations between the locomotive engineer and rail traffic controllers both before and after the derailment.\n*[http://ici.radio-canada.ca/nouvelles/science/2013/11/15/002-lac-megantic-tragedie-cles-decouverte.shtml 5 Keys to Understanding Lac Megantic disaster] (in French, infographics)\n*[http://www.weather.com/news/news/north-dakota-oil-by-rail-investigation BOOM: North America's Explosive Oil-by-Rail Problem] Investi